addtask.title: crud operations
addtask.description: CRUD operations are fundamental actions in data management: Create, Read, Update, and Delete. These operations form the basis for managing data within databases and applications, allowing users to insert, view, modify, and remove data. They are essential for dynamic applications, from user profile management and e-commerce inventory to social media posts and customer records.
